outputs.output_descr: Through its contribution to the Government priorities, this project is mainly focused on strengthening the coffee sector as a principal export commodity in Ethiopia through strengthening the National Coffee Platform. The project also supports the Ethiopian Commodity Exchange (ECX)  an organized market place for coffee where buyers and sellers come together to trade in an efficient, reliable and transparent market supplemented by innovation and technology. The project further extends to support Ministry of Trade in institutional capacity building with focus on export promotion.

project_descr: Support to private sector development is one of the major components of enhanced economic growth theme under the Ethiopia UNDAF.
